            "title": "霸王茶姬今晚於美納斯達克市場首掛 傳ADS以上限28美元定價",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">赴美國納斯達克市場上市的內地茶飲連鎖企業霸王茶姬，ADS將於今晚登場，市傳以上限28美元定價。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：霸王茶姬官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/833x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250311_FI_source-web_Chagee-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：霸王茶姬官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/833x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250311_FI_source-web_Chagee-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：霸王茶姬官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">霸王茶姬在美IPO由花旗、摩根士丹利、中金、德銀擔任主承銷商，日前《彭博》引述知情人士表示，對霸王茶姬招股表達有興趣認購的投資者，有意認購的股份數目已相等於上市發售股份的數倍，投資者包括中國的基金和環球長倉機構投資者。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">霸王茶姬成立於2017年，現已成為內地最大、增長最快的高端現製茶飲品牌。根據艾瑞諮詢的收據，截至去年底時，該公司網絡包括6440家門店，其中6284家位於內地。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240927_EN_Tea05_source-bp_.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240927_EN_Tea05_source-bp_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在2023年，該公司於內地及海外產生的GMV已達108億元(人民幣．下同)，2024年更增至295億元；以中國境內產生的GMB衡量，該公司是在2022年至2024年間於內地擁有超過1000家門店的所有茶飲品牌中增長最快的企業。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司於2024年淨收入達124.06億元，按年增長1.67倍；淨利潤25.15億元，淨利潤率20.3%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14861361-%e9%9c%b8%e7%8e%8b%e8%8c%b6%e5%a7%ac%e4%bb%8a%e6%99%9a%e6%96%bc%e7%be%8e%e7%b4%8d%e6%96%af%e9%81%94%e5%85%8b%e5%b8%82%e5%a0%b4%e9%a6%96%e6%8e%9b-%e5%82%b3ads%e4%bb%a5%e4%b8%8a%e9%99%9028%e7%be%8e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250311_FI_source-web_Chagee-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-17 12:00:45",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "滬深兩市股指早市齊轉升 房地產板塊受捧",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地A股今早低開高走，滬深兩市股指半日齊轉升，主要板塊升多跌少，內房股便是資金流入較明顯的板塊之一。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Shutterstock圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/bplib_20231123-123658_20231108_FI_source_licensed_中國樓市_中國房地產_shutterstock_704_source-licensed__704px.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Shutterstock圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/bplib_20231123-123658_20231108_FI_source_licensed_中國樓市_中國房地產_shutterstock_704_source-licensed__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Shutterstock圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早低開14點後，初段曾進一步試底，跌幅稍微擴大至跌17點、見3258點開始掉頭，早市全程反覆向上，中段已轉升，最高見3284點，升8點；滬指中午收報3282點，仍漲6點或0.21%。半日成交2724.88億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指相對跑輸，初段最低見9712點，跌62點，未幾已掉頭轉升，最高曾衝上9828點，升54點；深指中午收報9816點，升41點或0.42%，成交3447.92億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數則微跌不足1點或0.02%，收報3772點；創業板指數升11點或0.61%，報1918點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230629_FI_A股_9_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230629_FI_A股_9_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地房地產市場似漸有改善，部份城市如青島也推出利好樓市的新政，帶動房地產板塊造好。榮盛發展(02146)A股(002146.SZ)升4.35%，報1.44元；保利發展(06049)A股(600048.SH)也升4.19%，報9.2元；萬科(02202)A股(000002.SZ)升2.56%，報7.22元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14861302-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1%e5%85%a9%e5%b8%82%e8%82%a1%e6%8c%87%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e9%bd%8a%e8%bd%89%e5%8d%87-%e6%88%bf%e5%9c%b0%e7%94%a2%e6%9d%bf%e5%a1%8a%e5%8f%97%e6%8d%a7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-17 11:45:58",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美團小象超市傳開實體店  類型近盒馬鮮生",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內媒《36氪》報道，美團(03690)小象超市重新啟動線下業務，類型接近盒馬旗下的社區店品牌「盒馬NB」，或「盒馬鮮生」的大店模式。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"盒馬鮮生。資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/01/20240119_BLOG_-3.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"盒馬鮮生。資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/01/20240119_BLOG_-3.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">盒馬鮮生。資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">報道指，目前小象超市線下業務已啟動工程、營運等相關崗位的招聘，其中「輸出全國連鎖門店營運SOP」的中台相關負責人，招聘畫像是「餐飲、便利店、驛站等全國性連鎖業態的總部人員」。美團不予回應。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14861268-%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%98%e5%b0%8f%e8%b1%a1%e8%b6%85%e5%b8%82%e5%82%b3%e9%96%8b%e5%af%a6%e9%ab%94%e5%ba%97-%e9%a1%9e%e5%9e%8b%e8%bf%91%e7%9b%92%e9%a6%ac%e9%ae%ae%e7%94%9f",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230704-174452_source-web_%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%98%E9%85%8D%E9%80%81_source-web_.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-17 11:35:42",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股曾升292點   內房領升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股早段向好，恒生指數最低見21039，跌17點或0.08%，為暫時低位，隨即反覆向上，最高報21348，升292點或1.39%，為暫時高位。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指現報21349點，升292點或1.39%，恒生科技指數報4886，升90點或1.89% ; 恒生國企指數報7882，升103點或1.33%。   </p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內房領升，龍湖(00960)升5.09%，報10.8元 ; 中海外(00688)升4.44%，報14.6元，升幅居藍籌股首二位。華潤置地(01109)升1.87%，報27.3元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內需股跑輸，萬洲(00288)跌3.44%，報6.73元， ; 蒙牛(02319)跌2.73%，報19.22元; 為表現最差兩藍籌股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">巨子生物(02367)折讓9.5%配股，現跌4.75%，報70.15元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14861251-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e6%9b%be%e5%8d%87292%e9%bb%9e-%e5%85%a7%e6%88%bf%e9%a0%98%e5%8d%87",
